link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/hoc-phitop-gia-su-toan-gioi-lop-12-chuyen-luyen-thi-dai-hoc\/#1_Gia_su_day_Toan_12_%E2%80%93_On_luyen_thi_dai_hoc\" >1. Gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y To\u00e1n 12 &#8211; \u00d4n luy\u1ec7n th\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/hoc-phitop-gia-su-toan-gioi-lop-12-chuyen-luyen-thi-dai-hoc\/#2_Dia_chi_tim_gia_su_day_Toan_lop_12_o_dau_uy_tin\" >2. \u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 t\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 12 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u uy t\u00edn?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/hoc-phitop-gia-su-toan-gioi-lop-12-chuyen-luyen-thi-dai-hoc\/#3_Bang_gia_gia_su_mon_Toan_lop_12_%E2%80%93_on_luyen_thi_dai_hoc_o_Ha_Noi\" >3. B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 12 &#8211; \u00f4n luy\u1ec7n th\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/hoc-phitop-gia-su-toan-gioi-lop-12-chuyen-luyen-thi-dai-hoc\/#4_Nen_chon_gia_su_Toan_12_la_giao_vien_hay_sinh_vien\" >4. N\u00ean ch\u1ecdn gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n 12 l\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean hay sinh vi\u00ean<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/hoc-phitop-gia-su-toan-gioi-lop-12-chuyen-luyen-thi-dai-hoc\/#5_Quyen_loi_cua_gia_dinh_khi_den_voi_gia_su_Tri_Viet\" >5. Quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh khi \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"kk-star-ratings kksr-auto kksr-align-left kksr-valign-top\"\n    data-payload='{&quot;align&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;969&quot;,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;default&