          \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n                \n\n<div class=\"kksr-legend\" style=\"font-size: 19.2px;\">\n            <span class=\"kksr-muted\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 post<\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><em>Khi b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 con \u0111ang h\u1ecdc l\u1edbp 12 v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n <strong>t\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y To\u00e1n \u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea1i<\/strong> <strong>h\u1ecdc<\/strong> cho con? C\u00f3 l\u1ebd, vi\u1ec7c <strong>t\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 12 <\/strong>cho con qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, \u0110\u1ebfn v\u1edbi trung t\u00e2m <strong>gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t<\/strong> h\u1eb3n b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 <strong>gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 12<\/strong> <strong>t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong> \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng,l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng gia s\u01b0 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m trong <strong>luy\u1ec7n thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc m\u00f4n To\u00e1n. Gia s\u01b0 \u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc m\u00f4n To\u00e1n<\/strong> c\u1ee7a trung t\u00e2m Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t cam k\u1ebft v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 <strong>gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n \u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc<\/strong> s\u1ed1 1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-977 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/A\u0309nh-chu\u0323p-Ma\u0300n-hi\u0300nh-2018-09-24-lu\u0301c-4.45.44-CH.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"386\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/A\u0309nh-chu\u0323p-Ma\u0300n-hi\u0300nh-2018-09-24-lu\u0301c-4.45.44-CH.png 549w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/A\u0309nh-chu\u0323p-Ma\u0300n-hi\u0300nh-2018-09-24-lu\u0301c-4.45.44-CH-300x211.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 549px) 100vw, 549px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Gia_su_day_Toan_12_%E2%80%93_On_luyen_thi_dai_hoc\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>1. Gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y To\u00e1n 12 &#8211; \u00d4n luy\u1ec7n th\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">To\u00e1n l\u00e0 m\u00f4n h\u1ecdc r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u00f4n ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o trong k\u00ec thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc \u2013 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c\u00a0 \u0111\u1eddi con b\u1ea1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u00edt h\u1ecdc sinh g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n b\u1edfi m\u00f4n h\u1ecdc n\u00e0y, do nhi\u1ec1u nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">&#8211; Do thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c to\u00e1n t\u1eeb l\u1edbp 10, 11<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">&#8211; Do thi\u1ebfu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">&#8211; Do v\u1edbi th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean l\u1edbp qu\u00e1 \u00edt \u1ecfi \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp thu l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">&#8211; H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c thi m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c em kh\u00e1 b\u1ee1 ng\u1ee1<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">&#8211; C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea7n ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c ch\u01b0a hi\u1ec3u s\u00e2u nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i ng\u1ea1i h\u1ecfi th\u1ea7y c\u00f4, kh\u00f4ng trao \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 m\u01a1 h\u1ed3 v\u00e0 l\u00e2u d\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u ch\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp to\u00e1n 12 sa s\u00fat.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">&#8211; Ph\u1ee5 huynh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc <strong>To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 12<\/strong> c\u1ee7a con.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">==&gt;&gt; Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p cho ph\u1ee5 huynh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c em h\u1ecdc sinh l\u00e0 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng\u00a0<strong>gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n to\u00e1n l\u1edbp 12 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0\u00a0<\/strong>l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00ed.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-971\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/1525_co_lanh_1-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/1525_co_lanh_1-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/1525_co_lanh_1-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/1525_co_lanh_1.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><em>Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean d\u1ea1y to\u00e1n l\u1edbp 12 &#8211; \u00d4n thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Dia_chi_tim_gia_su_day_Toan_lop_12_o_dau_uy_tin\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>2. \u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 t\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 12 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u uy t\u00edn?<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">&#8211; Khi con b\u1ea1n \u0111ang h\u1ecdc l\u1edbp 12 th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 cho con h\u1eb3n kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, b\u1edfi lo l\u1eafng, tr\u0103n tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gia s\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u \u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ec3 con \u0111\u1ee7 ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o k\u00ec thi quan tr\u1ecdng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a con. \u0110\u1ec3 x\u00f3a tan n\u1ed7i lo c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1eadc ph\u1ee5 huynh th\u00ec <strong>gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t<\/strong> cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 gia s\u01b0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m trong <strong>d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m To\u00e1n 12<\/strong> c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc .<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">&#8211; <strong>\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n 12<\/strong> cam k\u1ebft trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e1c em:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">+\u00a0 Truy\u1ec1n h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa say m\u00ea h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp cho c\u00e1c em<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">+ \u00a0S\u1ebd c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c em t\u00ecm ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp m\u00f4n to\u00e1n t\u1ed1i \u01b0u, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">+ S\u1ebd th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c em tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c k\u00ec thi t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-818\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/gia-su\u031b-ha\u0300-no\u0323\u0302i-300x114.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"228\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/gia-su\u031b-ha\u0300-no\u0323\u0302i-300x114.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/gia-su\u031b-ha\u0300-no\u0323\u0302i-768x292.png 768w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/gia-su\u031b-ha\u0300-no\u0323\u0302i.png 820w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><em>Trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t &#8211; Chuy\u00ean cung c\u1ea5p gia s\u01b0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c m\u00f4n t\u1eeb l\u1edbp 1-12, \u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Bang_gia_gia_su_mon_Toan_lop_12_%E2%80%93_on_luyen_thi_dai_hoc_o_Ha_Noi\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>3. B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 12 &#8211; \u00f4n luy\u1ec7n th\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<table width=\"479\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\" width=\"479\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #282828; background-color: #ffff00; font-size: 120%;\"><strong>H\u1eccC PH\u00cd GIA S\u01af M\u00d4N TO\u00c1N L\u1edaP 12<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"160\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"160\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>Sinh vi\u00ean<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\n<td width=\"160\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"160\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>1 h\u1ecdc sinh<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"160\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">130.000 &#8211; 180.000<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"160\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">250.000 \u2013 300.000<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"160\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>2 h\u1ecdc sinh<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"160\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">200.000 &#8211; 250.000<\/span><\/td>\n<td width=\"160\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">350.000<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"160\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>&gt;= 3 h\u1ecdc sinh<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" width=\"160\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n<\/span><\/td>\n<td width=\"160\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">==&gt; Xem th\u00eam: <strong>B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 gia s\u01b0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c m\u00f4n<\/strong> h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c update m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t 2018 &amp; nh\u1eadn ngay 2 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc th\u1eed mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Nen_chon_gia_su_Toan_12_la_giao_vien_hay_sinh_vien\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>4. N\u00ean ch\u1ecdn gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n 12 l\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean hay sinh vi\u00ean <\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 12<\/strong> ch\u1ee9a 1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho k\u00ec thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc. V\u00ec v\u1eady, nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ee5 huynh b\u0103n kho\u0103n kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn gia s\u01b0 cho l\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean hay sinh vi\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong><em>\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean:<\/em><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">\u2666\u00a0H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f4ng, tr\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e2n l\u1eadp tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba b\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">\u2666\u00a0D\u1ea1y h\u1ecdc t\u1eadn t\u00ecnh, t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c em n\u00ean qu\u00fd ph\u1ee5 huynh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">\u2666\u00a0Chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n cao, uy t\u00edn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc, cao \u0111\u1eb3ng kh\u1ed1i A cho h\u1ecdc sinh l\u1edbp 12.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">\u2666\u00a0Th\u1eddi gian d\u1ea1y h\u1ecdc h\u01a1i h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u00ec c\u00e1c gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean th\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ea1y nhi\u1ec1u l\u1edbp, nhi\u1ec1u gia s\u01b0..<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">\u2666\u00a0H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed d\u1ea1y cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi gia s\u01b0 kh\u00e1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-972\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/nen-thue-sinh-vien-hay-giao-vien-300x169.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/nen-thue-sinh-vien-hay-giao-vien-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/nen-thue-sinh-vien-hay-giao-vien-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/nen-thue-sinh-vien-hay-giao-vien-1024x576.png 1024w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/nen-thue-sinh-vien-hay-giao-vien.png 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><em>N\u00ean thu\u00ea gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean hay gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean?<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong><em>\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean:<\/em><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">\u2666\u00a0\u0110ang v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng nh\u01b0 \u0110H S\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m HN, \u0110H B\u00e1ch Khoa, \u0110H Kinh t\u1ebf Qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n, \u0110H Ngo\u1ea1i Th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0110H Qu\u1ed1c gia H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\u2026<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">\u2666\u00a0Tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec7nh l\u1ec7ch nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc sinh n\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng n\u1eafm b\u1eaft, chia s\u1ebb, th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c em, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">\u2666\u00a0Tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 h\u1ecdc v\u1ea5n gi\u1ecfi, k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m t\u1ed1t, tr\u00ean 2 n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">\u2666\u00a0D\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i gi\u1edd h\u1ecdc linh ho\u1ea1t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">\u2666\u00a0Ch\u00ed ph\u00ed th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n kinh t\u1ebf gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">=&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;\u00a0<strong>Gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 12<\/strong> l\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean hay sinh vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf ri\u00eang, <strong>Gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t<\/strong> cung c\u00f3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 gia s\u01b0 bao g\u1ed3n c\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 vi\u00ean v\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1eadc ph\u1ee5 huynh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ph\u1ee5 huynh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 y\u00ean t\u00e2m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gia s\u01b0 c\u1ee7a trung t\u00e2m, b\u1edfi d\u00f9 l\u00e0 sinh th\u00ec c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m trong \u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc. C\u00e1c b\u1eadc ph\u1ee5 huynh h\u00e3y c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn <strong>gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n 12<\/strong> cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><i>\u00a0&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">===&gt;&gt;&gt; Xem ngay: Sinh vi\u00ean &#8211; Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean chuy\u00ean Ho\u00e1 l\u1edbp 12 &#8211; \u00d4n thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc tr\u00ean 8 \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">===&gt;&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam: <strong>Gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n Ti\u1ebfng anh<\/strong> cho con &#8211; T\u1eeb c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, \u0111\u1ebfn n\u00e2ng cao, luy\u1ec7n thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><i>\u00a0&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5_Quyen_loi_cua_gia_dinh_khi_den_voi_gia_su_Tri_Viet\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong>5. Quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh khi \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">\u2013\u00a0\u00a0<strong>Gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n 12<\/strong> \u00a0g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean \u0111ang gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng Ph\u1ed5 Th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 Sinh Vi\u00ean \u01b0u t\u00fa c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng: \u0110H S\u01b0 Ph\u1ea1m, \u0110H B\u00e1ch Khoa, \u0110H Ngo\u1ea1i Th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0110H Kinh T\u1ebf,DHQG,\u2026<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">\u2013 Ki\u1ec3m tra tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">\u2013\u00a0Gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y th\u1eed<strong>\u00a0<\/strong>2 bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gia s\u01b0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">\u2013\u00a0Gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc sinh l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t g\u1ed1c, ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c c\u0103n b\u1ea3n trong v\u00f2ng 10 bu\u1ed5i d\u1ea1y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">\u2013 Cung c\u1ea5p gi\u1ecfi, nhanh nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5i gia s\u01b0 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c n\u1ebfu ph\u1ee5 huynh th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">.- Gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y c\u1ee7a gia s\u01b0 v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc sinh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p khi c\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">\u2013 H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n tr\u1ecdn \u0111\u1eddi d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 gia s\u01b0.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-973\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/quyen-loi-khi-den-voi-trung-tam-gia-su-binh-minh-300x169.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/quyen-loi-khi-den-voi-trung-tam-gia-su-binh-minh-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/quyen-loi-khi-den-voi-trung-tam-gia-su-binh-minh-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/quyen-loi-khi-den-voi-trung-tam-gia-su-binh-minh-1024x576.png 1024w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/quyen-loi-khi-den-voi-trung-tam-gia-su-binh-minh.png 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">=&gt;&gt;Xem th\u00eam c\u00e1c m\u00f4n kh\u00e1c:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><strong style=\"font-style: italic;\">Gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n Ng\u1eef v\u0103n l\u1edbp 12<\/strong><i> chuy\u00ean \u00f4n luy\u1ec7n thi \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc 2019<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><em><strong>Gia s\u01b0 luy\u1ec7n thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc c\u1ea5p t\u1ed1c m\u00f4n V\u1eadt L\u00fd<\/strong> &#8211; T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c, luy\u1ec7n chuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1.<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\"><b>TRUNG T\u00c2M<\/b>\u00a0<b>GIA S\u01af<\/b>\u00a0<b>TR\u00cd VI\u1ec6T<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">\u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 : T\u00f2a N03 &#8211; Ph\u1ed1 Tr\u1ea7n Qu\u00fd Ki\u00ean, Q.C\u1ea7u Gi\u1ea5y, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">Email: <a style=\"color: #282828;\" href=\"mailto:giasubinhminh.eduvn@gmail.com\"><span class=\"s2\">giasubinhminh.eduvn@gmail.com<\/span><\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #282828;\">Li\u00ean h\u1ec7: 0962.005.996 ho\u1eb7c 0987.005.996<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Khi b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 con \u0111ang h\u1ecdc l\u1edbp 12 v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y To\u00e1n \u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc cho con? C\u00f3 l\u1ebd, vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":974,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","f